validator.py — Node schema and canon promotion validator

Validates PSCL YAML nodes against:

1. Required fields (schema completeness)
1. Five-field minimal form (compression test)
1. Canon promotion gates (compression, transfer, failure, safety, retrieval)
1. Structural consistency (neighbor IDs, transfer IDs exist in corpus)

Exit codes:
0 — all checks passed
1 — warnings only
2 — errors found
